++ What is ANTHOLOGY?

ANTHOLOGY is a 31-day event wherein each day of October, a horror SCP is posted, each by a different author. All SCPs are bound by the theme "ABCs of Death" -- the challenge was for each author to write an SCP based off a word beginning with their assigned letter. There's no interconnectedness or storyline here -- aside from the arrangement, stories will diverge in any number of ways, or be spread across any topic or canon. 

There's something for everyone here. So long as it is nightmares you seek.
